{
  "day": "1",
  "heading": "Drive from Rishikesh to Dhak / Karchi",
  "sub_heading": "Drive distance: 255 km | Drive Duration: 9-10 hours | Pick up point for Indiahikes trekkers: Live Free Hostel, Rishikesh | Pick up Time: 5.30 am | Location of Indiahikes basecamp: Karchi / Dhak",
  "details": "Transport will be arranged at 5.30 AM sharp. The costs are Rs 1400 (additional 5% GST) per trekker (one-way) for the journey from Rishikesh to Dhak / Karchi.  Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek."
}

